How This Model Is Trained

This model is trained with HCP-Diffusion. And the auto-training framework is maintained by DeepGHS Team.

Why Some Preview Images Not Look Like Siege Arknights

All the prompt texts used on the preview images (which can be viewed by clicking on the images) are automatically generated using clustering algorithms based on feature information extracted from the training dataset. The seed used during image generation is also randomly generated, and the images have not undergone any selection or modification. As a result, there is a possibility of the mentioned issues occurring.

In practice, based on our internal testing, most models that experience such issues perform better in actual usage than what is seen in the preview images. The only thing you may need to do is fine-tune the tags you use.

It's an interesting experiment conducted by our team, and for this purpose, we have developed a complete set of software infrastructure, including data filtering, automatic training, and automated publishing. Therefore, if possible, we would appreciate more feedback or suggestions as they are highly valuable to us.

The reason why this is a beta sums up to this bad backgrounds, and difficult shapes more on this and things to get around this are below until I train a proper version.
This was trained on the tron legacy movie primarily making most backgrounds grid like (minimalistic, pixel, square) so further edits are necessary. Can be worked around by proper prompting.
Also since it was trained with a lot of black clothes in dark areas I recommend a style to easily show more definition in your characters.
If someone has an idea or just knows a gallery for tron like images that would be appreciated.

To help give some definition to body shapes I did play with using atomic hips and hyperfusion
https://civitai.com/models/16928/hyperfusion-280k-images

Goals:
Stop messing up backgrounds
Turn any garment of clothing tron like
No other lora necessary for body details

items.name: Silhouette Synthesis 逆光幻境
items.description:
Goodbye to the fucking internet-famous face shit！

The biggest issue with the current large models in terms of lighting is the separation of "people" and "objects". It's as if a person was pasted into a scene, missing the depth that lighting brings, which is a significant reason why it feels so AI-esque.

So, I began trying to improve this. If one were to delve deep to address this, the top priority would be the excessive or unreasonable lighting on the characters. The best way to solve this would be to create ample backlighting, allowing the character and the environment to blend more seamlessly.

Inspired by 'Blade Runner 2049', I decided to showcase my model with a subdued color tone, a style with distinct dark and bright contrasts. I named it 'Silhouette Synthesis'.

目前的大模型在光影层面最大的问题是“人”与“物”的分离，像是在一个场景里拼贴了一个人进去，光影带来的层次感是缺失的，这也是ai感十足的重要原因。

于是我开始试着去改善这一问题。这个问题如果想要去细分解决，那最优先应该解决的就是人物身上过度或者不合理的光照，那么解决这个问题最好的方式就是制造足够的背光面积，这样可以让人物和景物更好的融为一体。

同时，基于bladerunner 2049的启示，我决定用一种色调压抑、阴暗对比明显的光影风格来展示我的模型，同时起名为 Silhouette Synthesis。

items.name: 【再世】next life-牛振华
items.description:
这是群星再世第八十期，以后会不定期出去世的群星Lora，以纪念他们。

他是最会演电影的相声演员之一，牛振华创作和表演过80多段相声，包括《放心地飞吧》、《一路风波》、《阴差阳错》。他都是担任逗哏，但效果平平。牛振华进入影视行业是1987年，机会得来还有赖于好友冯巩。有一天冯巩带他去老导演谢添家作客，冯巩已经定下出演谢添的新剧《那五》，但配角索七的演员一直没定下来，原计划是让梁冠华来出演这一角色，谢添看到当时还不算胖的牛振华就说，你来演吧。不太自信的牛振华，由此接触影视表演。

后来找牛振华演戏的剧组越来越多，影响到他在空政歌舞团的工作，在和家人，领导商量犹豫了几个月之后，他决定离开，九十年代初正式转业到中国广播艺术团，也就是冯巩所在的团。1992年，牛振华的又一位伯乐出现了。还是冯巩，带牛振华去黄建新导演家玩儿，当时黄建新正准备执导电影《站直啰，别趴下》，冯巩是主演。聊到扮演配角张永武的演员，黄建新说副导演找了一个叫什么华的胖子。冯巩问，不会就是牛振华吧？黄建新看着牛振华说，应该是，我看着挺合适。

后来依靠《背靠背，脸对脸》拿到国际影帝，再后来，牛振华还出演过电影《埋伏》、《宋家皇朝》和《谁说我不在乎》，尽管都是配角，但表演能力仍然让人记忆深刻。

2004年，因酒驾车祸追尾去世，享年48岁。

items.name: Final Fantasy XII Architecture LoRA
items.description:
I have a form for requests; check it out if you want to request a character.

A LoRA trained on architectural images from Final Fantasy XII. Trained on NAI. Tested at 1.0-1.2 strength.

  • Trigger word is "12style".

  • Adding words like "castle", "city", or "desert" might aid in approximating the intended style.

  • Images of Archades' cityscapes were separately categorized with the tag "archades" in training, so add this tag while generating cities.

Very experimental, and I'm looking to retrain this if I can collect more varied data.

Created for the architecture collaboration. Check out my Discord if you want to take part in future collaborations (or yell at me about requests.)

All the prompt texts used on the preview images (which can be viewed by clicking on the images) are automatically generated using clustering algorithms based on feature information extracted from the training dataset. The seed used during image generation is also randomly generated, and the images have not undergone any selection or modification. As a result, there is a possibility of the mentioned issues occurring.

In practice, based on our internal testing, most models that experience such issues perform better in actual usage than what is seen in the preview images. The only thing you may need to do is fine-tune the tags you use.

Our model has been published on huggingface repository - CyberHarem/flandre_scarlet_touhou, where models of all the steps are saved. Also, we published the training dataset on huggingface dataset - CyberHarem/flandre_scarlet_touhou, which may be helpful to you.

Our model's entire process, from data crawling, training, to generating preview images and publishing, is 100% automated without any human intervention. It's an interesting experiment conducted by our team, and for this purpose, we have developed a complete set of software infrastructure, including data filtering, automatic training, and automated publishing. Therefore, if possible, we would appreciate more feedback or suggestions as they are highly valuable to us.

very long hair, low-tied long hair

Our model's entire process, from data crawling, training, to generating preview images and publishing, is 100% automated without any human intervention.
